-- MOVES-Fidelity Worldwide Investment hires Peter Horrell from Barclays
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bangalore
-- Wed Oct 08, 2014 08:23AM EDT
-- None



Oct 8 (Reuters) - Asset manager Fidelity Worldwide Investment named Peter Horrell as managing director of its UK business, effective April 1, 2015.

Horrell joins from Barclays Plc <BARC.L>, where he headed the wealth & investment management business.